summary: The Digital.gov.au AI Policy document's content is currently inaccessible.  All four sections ('Implementation', 'Enable and Prepare', 'Engage Responsibly', and 'Evolve and Integrate') return HTTP2 Protocol Errors, indicating the website is experiencing issues or the pages have been moved.
